{"tid":1650180,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"忘記蛋糕，盡情開花！！","createTime":"2019-10-13T00:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T05:47:58.000Z","uid":158857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e3be9b851dd0dd72cbf0565de99b3266a6770207","tid":1650180,"uid":158857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:01:57.000Z","msg":"蛋糕撚係抵屌！但宜家唔係屌人的時候！<br />\n<br />\n事有緩急先後！忘記彼此之間的芥蒂！<br />\n<br />\n盡力去做好件事！呢一刻最重要唔係指責！<br />\n<br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">團結</span><br />\n<br />\n講多次係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">團結</span><br />\n<br />\n只有團結我地先有機會勝利<br />\n<br />\n第一日已經講核爆都唔割！<br />\n<br />\n點可以因爲蛋糕而一團散沙！<br />\n<br />\n仲有幾個鐘就開花！<br />\n<br />\n希望大家集中討論朵花點先可以開得靚！<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港！時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"d5e71d7f34ce59925b419325a2f0b4464528a38e","tid":1650180,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:02:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e626736a333681428ee7a3b74ca4c9a2039b05b1","tid":1650180,"uid":158857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:03:03.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"e60e47bac963397b5d0a1316cdf2dc88eec7bd3a","tid":1650180,"uid":158857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:03:14.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"447bd3964b00dbb382dc91d70c5a84ba76584483","tid":1650180,"uid":158857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:03:27.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"af1f9d607f9de5f894b069146c14833c311fb4d9","tid":1650180,"uid":158857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:03:38.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"9b29ff558e3d4301b55736efe8029eaf67b0343d","tid":1650180,"uid":158857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T00:03:49.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"fc84ea6f0605cd1991155454cc8ca7de9910b63e","tid":1650180,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:47:58.000